          <div class="col-md-6 col-12 main_header_left">
            <p>Welcome to AKweather App</p>
            <h1>Get The Letest <span style="color: rgb(47, 47, 253);"> Weather</span> Info Of your City</h1>
            <a href="/weather"><button
                style="border: none; padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem; font-size: 1.4rem; border-radius: 2rem; text-transform: uppercase; box-shadow: 0 10px 8px -8px rgb(0, 49, 184); outline: none;">Check
